[SPEAKER_00] I tu vidimo,

634
00:43:56,000 --> 00:43:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] ne dolazi i materijalna blagost

635
00:43:58,000 --> 00:43:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] u njegov život.

636
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Doista,

637
00:44:00,000 --> 00:44:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je rekao,

638
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] tražite Božje kraljevstvo,

639
00:44:02,000 --> 00:44:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] njegovu pravidnost,

640
00:44:04,000 --> 00:44:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] a sve ono što će vam se nadobrati.

641
00:44:06,000 --> 00:44:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad posložimo istravno sloje,

642
00:44:07,000 --> 00:44:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] to je bila tema prije dva tjedna,

643
00:44:09,000 --> 00:44:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] onda se ovom materijalno posloži.

644
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno iz iskustva,

645
00:44:14,000 --> 00:44:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] rada se ljudima,

646
00:44:16,000 --> 00:44:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] biblijski zakon nisu stalni.

647
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odjedno,

648
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] vidimo Tobiju,

649
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] koja je u braku,

650
00:44:24,000 --> 00:44:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] koja ima uspišan biznis,

651
00:44:26,000 --> 00:44:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] gledajući ljudskim očima,

652
00:44:29,000 --> 00:44:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] koja ima autoritet,

653
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] što je najvažnije,

654
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] da stane pred Boga i zagovora,

655
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] imamo izgrađeno čovjeka.

656
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to je proces koji mi svi moramo proći.

657
00:44:39,000 --> 00:44:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] i sad imamo Tobiju,

658
00:44:44,000 --> 00:44:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji se vraća slove ocu.

659
00:44:46,000 --> 00:44:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, nakon,

660
00:44:48,000 --> 00:44:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] on dolazi,

661
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] uzima žuć prvo da raka,

662
00:44:54,000 --> 00:44:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] i sa žuć od rime,

663
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] i sa žući premaže slove ocu oči

664
00:44:58,000 --> 00:45:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] i odnosuje progledaj na taj način.

665
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je simbolika.

666
00:45:02,000 --> 00:45:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta simbolizira žuć?

667
00:45:04,000 --> 00:45:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gorčina, tako.

668
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Često nam u prvom situaciji,

669
00:45:08,000 --> 00:45:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] gorke teške,

670
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] od dvoje oči da progledamo.

671
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Doslovci.

672
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to se dogodilo sa tobim ocem,

673
00:45:16,000 --> 00:45:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] gdje on ozdravlja,

674
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] i do tad je pas više za njima,

675
00:45:20,000 --> 00:45:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] a tada pas prestajen za njima.

676
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Doslovci je cijela bitelj je ozdravljena.

677
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je moguć.

678
00:45:27,000 --> 00:45:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to se može dogoditi po vama.

679
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nuzno je bilo i da Rafa onda ode.

680
00:45:36,000 --> 00:45:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

681
00:45:37,000 --> 00:45:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite, kako bi se mi osjećalo prema čovjeku,

682
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji vam je,

683
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] doznice, vas je podigo potpuno,

684
00:45:46,000 --> 00:45:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] osigurano ga života s svih strana.

685
00:45:48,000 --> 00:45:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne osjećali, zahvalimo se nekoj.

686
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

687
00:45:50,000 --> 00:45:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] jedna priljubav, Rafa, osti sve.

688
00:45:52,000 --> 00:45:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Često Bog, ona baš takvu osobu,

689
00:45:56,000 --> 00:45:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] nakon što ste mi postigli tu zrednost tu dalje,

690
00:45:59,000 --> 00:46:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] iz vaših života.

691
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

692
00:46:01,000 --> 00:46:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mislite zašto?

693
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo izmišljite, znam me kasno.

694
00:46:04,000 --> 00:46:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

695
00:46:06,000 --> 00:46:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog nareziva.

696
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ta osoba vam se dovala do Boga,

697
00:46:15,000 --> 00:46:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali onda će doći jedan period

698
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem će te vi i doslovce more

699
00:46:20,000 --> 00:46:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] sami dolaziti do Boga.

700
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste došli do zrednosti.

701
00:46:24,000 --> 00:46:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tu sam imao sliku,

702
00:46:26,000 --> 00:46:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] dok sam molio za to,

703
00:46:27,000 --> 00:46:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] gospod mi naredim sliku u molitvi,

704
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] baš dok sam molio za ovaj zadnji dio.

705
00:46:32,000 --> 00:46:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus čini velika čudesa.

706
00:46:37,000 --> 00:46:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Apostoli su oko njega

707
00:46:39,000 --> 00:46:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] i dolaze na večer

708
00:46:41,000 --> 00:46:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] i vidi da ovu molim.

709
00:46:43,000 --> 00:46:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] I u njima

710
00:46:45,000 --> 00:46:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] se doslovce razvija ta znatišnja.

711
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni se vačaju.

712
00:46:49,000 --> 00:46:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što se događa preko nama,

713
00:46:50,000 --> 00:46:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] a to je da su bubaci ozdravljeni,

714
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] kromi ustaju u obsjedut,

715
00:46:53,000 --> 00:46:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] oslobođeni i to,

716
00:46:55,000 --> 00:46:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] ima veze sa tim što on radi po noći.

717
00:46:58,000 --> 00:47:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čisto ljuga, oni su mene ribani,

718
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] nisu puno pametovni.

719
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su vidili on tu po noći,

720
00:47:03,000 --> 00:47:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] ide tenisa i mrvratu,

721
00:47:04,000 --> 00:47:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] crpi snanje,

722
00:47:05,000 --> 00:47:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] kad se spusti uvjetro,

723
00:47:06,000 --> 00:47:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] svi ozdravljaju.

724
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] i dolaze i to budi

725
00:47:09,000 --> 00:47:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] i Ljuga kaže:

726
00:47:10,000 --> 00:47:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Nauči nas molit."

727
00:47:11,000 --> 00:47:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što je pripa za svakog

728
00:47:13,000 --> 00:47:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] duhovnika i pratitelja,

729
00:47:14,000 --> 00:47:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] je da osiguram svojima

730
00:47:16,000 --> 00:47:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] da oni ne budu toliko njegove učenici,

731
00:47:19,000 --> 00:47:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] nego da postavljaju učenici

732
00:47:21,000 --> 00:47:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] duha svetoga.

733
00:47:22,000 --> 00:47:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su pravi kako on pleć

734
00:47:24,000 --> 00:47:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] pred Božem podlaže,

735
00:47:25,000 --> 00:47:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] podlaže svoga oca

736
00:47:26,000 --> 00:47:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] i tu crkvi snanje.

737
00:47:27,000 --> 00:47:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] I oni njih nauči,

738
00:47:28,000 --> 00:47:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] da njih je naučio oče naš.

739
00:47:30,000 --> 00:47:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ta svika morala tako snažno ostati u njega,

740
00:47:33,000 --> 00:47:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] da onda kada je on uvora

741
00:47:35,000 --> 00:47:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] i otišao,

742
00:47:36,000 --> 00:47:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] gospodinu mi je pokazio

743
00:47:38,000 --> 00:47:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] odale dvije situacije.

744
00:47:39,000 --> 00:47:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Petar je tad bio najbliži njemu,

745
00:47:42,000 --> 00:47:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] imamo Petar u dijelama apostolskim,

746
00:47:44,000 --> 00:47:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] već sa autoritetom, izgrađeni,

747
00:47:46,000 --> 00:47:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] pada u zanus,

748
00:47:48,000 --> 00:47:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] on zna kako moliti,

749
00:47:50,000 --> 00:47:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] moliti, Bogu pokazuje viziju

750
00:47:52,000 --> 00:47:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] i nakon te vizije počinja mrčeni povrat.

751
00:47:54,000 --> 00:47:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što su oni upili od njega,

752
00:47:56,000 --> 00:47:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] su kasnije mogli napraviti

753
00:47:58,000 --> 00:47:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] i to je mijenjalo svijet.

754
00:47:59,000 --> 00:48:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dalje mi je gospodin pokazao

755
00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ivana,

756
00:48:03,000 --> 00:48:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] on je na otoku Patunstvu u 100. godini,

757
00:48:05,000 --> 00:48:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] opet pada u zanos

758
00:48:07,000 --> 00:48:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] i gleda Boga Otca, gleda Isusa,

759
00:48:09,000 --> 00:48:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] čovjek zna moliti,

760
00:48:11,000 --> 00:48:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] zna kako moliti i tu nasta je knjiga okrivenja.

761
00:48:13,000 --> 00:48:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što su oni upijali

762
00:48:15,000 --> 00:48:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] gledanoči njega,

763
00:48:17,000 --> 00:48:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] kad se on povukao,

764
00:48:19,000 --> 00:48:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] oni su shvatili da to je Oni Bogu.

765
00:48:21,000 --> 00:48:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to ja želim mogli igrazova

766
00:48:23,000 --> 00:48:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] prijavlja obama natalatu ruki.

767
00:48:25,000 --> 00:48:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Elis da je trčao

768
00:48:27,000 --> 00:48:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] sa prorakom Ilijom,

769
00:48:29,000 --> 00:48:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] nije učinio nijedno čude

770
00:48:31,000 --> 00:48:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] dok Ilija bio živ.

771
00:48:33,000 --> 00:48:33,000
[UNKNOWN] I kada Ilija

772
00:48:33,000 --> 00:48:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] na sameti bacio plašta njega,

773
00:48:35,000 --> 00:48:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno kad je bio znesen,

774
00:48:37,000 --> 00:48:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] oni išu ponoviti Ilino čudo.

775
00:48:39,000 --> 00:48:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ilija sad dadao čuda,

776
00:48:41,000 --> 00:48:41,000
[UNKNOWN] bacio plašta njega,

777
00:48:41,000 --> 00:48:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] sad ja treba biti prorok.

778
00:48:43,000 --> 00:48:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ilija je prije nego što je Umar udario

779
00:48:45,000 --> 00:48:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] odna puta

780
00:48:47,000 --> 00:48:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] po rjecu na Levan i reka je

781
00:48:49,000 --> 00:48:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] odna se razgijenila.

782
00:48:50,000 --> 00:48:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad dolazi Elizei,

783
00:48:52,000 --> 00:48:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] prova,

784
00:48:53,000 --> 00:48:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] lupa i kaže:

785
00:48:54,000 --> 00:48:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Gdje je Jakar Bog Jeji?"

786
00:48:56,000 --> 00:48:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Toš nije bio Nego Bog.

787
00:48:58,000 --> 00:49:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je samo pro materočini brošao,

788
00:49:00,000 --> 00:49:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali Bog je razbojio uvodu.

789
00:49:02,000 --> 00:49:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on je vidio:

790
00:49:04,000 --> 00:49:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Tata, bre, to je Bog moj."

791
00:49:06,000 --> 00:49:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I od tad on dijelo je ime Bože.

792
00:49:09,000 --> 00:49:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je povudao veliku milost

793
00:49:11,000 --> 00:49:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] da sam mogao od osnovce duhovno odrastat

794
00:49:13,000 --> 00:49:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] uz velitarne vjere.

795
00:49:15,000 --> 00:49:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću još to slavno upozlao sam ljude

796
00:49:17,000 --> 00:49:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] i u Ikrisu,

797
00:49:19,000 --> 00:49:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] imao sam prije kada sa mnijem baradom

798
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Josipom Očarom,

799
00:49:22,000 --> 00:49:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam karizmaticno

800
00:49:23,000 --> 00:49:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] promatratnih u njihovom djelogu.

801
00:49:25,000 --> 00:49:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Puno sam učio od njih.

802
00:49:27,000 --> 00:49:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nastala sam sve to

803
00:49:29,000 --> 00:49:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] na svoj način provoditi u dijelu sam.

804
00:49:32,000 --> 00:49:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se ima znači s novima?

805
00:49:34,000 --> 00:49:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni ne postignu do ove to bine razine.

806
00:49:36,000 --> 00:49:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dalje,

807
00:49:37,000 --> 00:49:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] kad ih nešto zaboli će istražiti

808
00:49:39,000 --> 00:49:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] staje ima u balnička.

809
00:49:40,000 --> 00:49:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je mene Bože ba umarao na jednom godinu.

810
00:49:43,000 --> 00:49:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je rekao:

811
00:49:45,000 --> 00:49:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni koji vjeraju mene

812
00:49:47,000 --> 00:49:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] na nemoću ti će staviti ruke

813
00:49:49,000 --> 00:49:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] i oni će odraditi.

814
00:49:50,000 --> 00:49:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se od vas izborio

815
00:49:52,000 --> 00:49:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] da stvaraju srce u tom podijem?

816
00:49:54,000 --> 00:49:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna prva će da ima djece

817
00:49:55,000 --> 00:49:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] i bit će vam staviti.

818
00:49:56,000 --> 00:49:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] staviti.

819
00:49:58,000 --> 00:50:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rastite motoritetu djetita Božnika.

820
00:50:02,000 --> 00:50:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što bih htio za kraj postaviti kao jako važno.

821
00:50:07,000 --> 00:50:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi često i dođu

822
00:50:10,000 --> 00:50:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] do sazrijevanja

823
00:50:11,000 --> 00:50:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] i postavaju zrijevanje

824
00:50:13,000 --> 00:50:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] i onda njiho odukovno spada.

825
00:50:15,000 --> 00:50:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

826
00:50:16,000 --> 00:50:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dok je bila stiska,

827
00:50:17,000 --> 00:50:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] dok im je puno tog trebalo,

828
00:50:19,000 --> 00:50:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] su jako redno je prednagolili.

829
00:50:21,000 --> 00:50:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad su došle od svišanja

830
00:50:23,000 --> 00:50:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] sve je stalo.

831
00:50:24,000 --> 00:50:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tobijan nije bio takav.

832
00:50:27,000 --> 00:50:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njegov život u prisve kaže:

833
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Tu doživje často starost,

834
00:50:31,000 --> 00:50:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] často pokopa svog tasne žmonicu,

835
00:50:33,000 --> 00:50:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] te naslijedio votak njihov,

836
00:50:35,000 --> 00:50:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] kao što je naslijedio jočer.

837
00:50:37,000 --> 00:50:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Umrjeo je k Matani u 127. godini života.

838
00:50:41,000 --> 00:50:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prije nego što je izdaknuo,

839
00:50:43,000 --> 00:50:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] dozna je za kropas njene,

840
00:50:45,000 --> 00:50:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] koju razoviše na Dukadonu Zoret i Asuner."

841
00:50:47,000 --> 00:50:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je biti varbalatak?

842
00:50:49,000 --> 00:50:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je ostao vjeran Bogu do kraja.

843
00:50:51,000 --> 00:50:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] A Isus je rekao jednu rečenicu

844
00:50:54,000 --> 00:50:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] o kojoj bi svaki od nas trebalo razmišljati

845
00:50:56,000 --> 00:50:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] svaki dan.

846
00:50:57,000 --> 00:51:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Komu se ne do kraja bići spašeni?

847
00:51:00,000 --> 00:51:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Do kraja ostati Boži.

848
00:51:03,000 --> 00:51:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bez kompromisa, živjeti svetom."

849
00:51:06,000 --> 00:51:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to je Tobija napravio.

850
00:51:08,000 --> 00:51:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je bitnola činjenica na Dukadonu?

851
00:51:10,000 --> 00:51:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato živio je kraj i smrt svojih neprijatelj.

852
00:51:13,000 --> 00:51:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Naši neprijatelj džava.

853
00:51:15,000 --> 00:51:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on će se boriti protiv našeg spisanja od toga kraja.

854
00:51:19,000 --> 00:51:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pobjeđuju samo oni koji su ustavili.

855
00:51:22,000 --> 00:51:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što vama, pošto je ovo zadnji susret prije ljetnoj pauze,

856
00:51:29,000 --> 00:51:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] idući put dođite opetak, bit će velika dugu na odnova.

857
00:51:32,000 --> 00:51:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Za kraj, a ovo je zadnji ovakvi susret.

858
00:51:34,000 --> 00:51:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Preko netak, imate priliku, sad s ovog razinom

859
00:51:39,000 --> 00:51:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ćemo se došli tić svoju dugovu stolako.

860
00:51:41,000 --> 00:51:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz osobni odnos s Bogom.

861
00:51:43,000 --> 00:51:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ili paš stolako nisko.

862
00:51:45,000 --> 00:51:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad dolazim na test vaša vjerovosti u stranost.

863
00:51:50,000 --> 00:51:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Slako je bilo dok ste imali susret, pa čladanje, pa nam je pa stalno to nešto povlači.

864
00:51:54,000 --> 00:51:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] U ljeti ćeš biti ti s Bogom vjera na jednu.

865
00:51:58,000 --> 00:52:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi, a vjerujte mi, svaki tjedan radim se s ljudima svih generacija.

866
00:52:05,000 --> 00:52:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sa opšednotima, bolesnima, ranjenima, zdravima.

867
00:52:10,000 --> 00:52:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Doslovno se od prve godine do osamdesete.

868
00:52:15,000 --> 00:52:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako sad, kao mladi, radite na svojim okolnosti i odnosu s Bogom,

869
00:52:21,000 --> 00:52:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] stvaran sa svim žalom, napravit ćete tako dobar temelj za svoj boličovit.

870
00:52:26,000 --> 00:52:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte dopustiti da vam žalo to krade.

871
00:52:30,000 --> 00:52:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka odluka koju donosite je bitna.

872
00:52:34,000 --> 00:52:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka loša navika oko koju se trudite se riješiti je važna.

873
00:52:41,000 --> 00:52:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imaće utjece ne na vas, ne na vaše buduće obitelji.

874
00:52:44,000 --> 00:52:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Živite sve to.

875
00:52:47,000 --> 00:52:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mudri Samovo, popolednikom knjezi, kaže ovako:

876
00:52:51,000 --> 00:52:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I sjećaj se svoga stvoritela u danima svoje mladosti.

877
00:52:55,000 --> 00:53:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prije njegov dođu svoje dani i prispiju godine kada će šeći ne mimo misl."

878
00:53:01,000 --> 00:53:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate kakvu žal i bol osjećaju ljudi koji upoznaju Boga sa 30-40 godina?

879
00:53:07,000 --> 00:53:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad shvatneš, šta su sve moline?

880
00:53:09,000 --> 00:53:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nisu.

881
00:53:11,000 --> 00:53:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] A mama je dano.

882
00:53:13,000 --> 00:53:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ove godine sam absolvent, imao sam vreme na svaku temu.

883
00:53:19,000 --> 00:53:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Baš svaka tema koju sam vam imao, ugotovo u drugom dijelo bila izboljena.

884
00:53:23,000 --> 00:53:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bolio sam da spojavim, pokaže šta vam sad sprema.

885
00:53:27,000 --> 00:53:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govorili smo s polnosti.

886
00:53:29,000 --> 00:53:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govorili smo o tom kako zdravo živjeti brak.

887
00:53:31,000 --> 00:53:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Voda kroz temu kako podići zdravu kršćansku obitelj, orlovskih kršćana.

888
00:53:37,000 --> 00:53:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govorili smo o tome kako se odnositi prema radu i novcu.

889
00:53:41,000 --> 00:53:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako izgraditi osoba na odnos Bogom?

890
00:53:43,000 --> 00:53:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije da vas proziramo.

891
00:53:45,000 --> 00:53:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zanija me koliko od vas ono, koliko nadova i pamijemo se time.

892
00:53:50,000 --> 00:53:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Knjige koje smo prozirali, kao šta obnova kršćanska obitelj, recimo.

893
00:53:55,000 --> 00:53:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Baš mi zanija tada ikona pamijen.

894
00:53:57,000 --> 00:54:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Al to moli si koliko ćemo i kako našem dobiti.

895
00:54:03,000 --> 00:54:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govorili smo stavu prema novcu.

896
00:54:09,000 --> 00:54:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moje od vas će se baviti jednog danačina svoje filme.

897
00:54:12,000 --> 00:54:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Biblija na 2350 stranica govori o novcu.

898
00:54:16,000 --> 00:54:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima knjiga "O pravda ovcem za katolik".

899
00:54:19,000 --> 00:54:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima ta predavanja, bit će sad sve na internetu.

900
00:54:22,000 --> 00:54:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljeto vam je prilika da sve to dobro što ste mogli tu primiti,

901
00:54:26,000 --> 00:54:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] i što je posijano, to nese plod.

902
00:54:29,000 --> 00:54:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] A već sam to rekao na izdavu, ja kao agronom znam da sjeme kad se posijano,

903
00:54:35,000 --> 00:54:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] ako se ne zaljeva, ne gnoje, ako se ne čisti kovar okoljega, neće nikakva patrota.

904
00:54:40,000 --> 00:54:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to će se ovdje dovoliti.

905
00:54:42,000 --> 00:54:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nate kako lako?

906
00:54:43,000 --> 00:54:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Postane duže spati, izađe vam, padni u grijeh, odgodi ispovjed, pričajte malo, pričekaj malo i već si tu.

907
00:54:51,000 --> 00:54:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sve što sam gavili, kroz ovu godinu, opet ispočenika.

908
00:54:56,000 --> 00:55:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] A kad imaš spoznajno, lijeka, onda je puno teži.

909
00:55:00,000 --> 00:55:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema kad nemaš.

910
00:55:01,000 --> 00:55:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljeto je za tebe izazov.

911
00:55:04,000 --> 00:55:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da postaneš svet ili napadeš još dubrije.

912
00:55:07,000 --> 00:55:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sa Bogom nema šave, vaše vječosti opitanje.

913
00:55:11,000 --> 00:55:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Trebalo biti radnost, nije, trebalo biti budni.

914
00:55:14,000 --> 00:55:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Duhovni zakon je sustavni.

915
00:55:17,000 --> 00:55:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zvrši ovih, sa citatom za vas.

916
00:55:23,000 --> 00:55:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dalje Zulkan, kad je tu molil na izdjevu,

917
00:55:27,000 --> 00:55:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] on je vaš proveren i koordinatorjem.

918
00:55:31,000 --> 00:55:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi od vas su bili na izdjevu sad, i Boga mi dao lika smjerica za liko životinu.

919
00:55:36,000 --> 00:55:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima je sliku puteva.

920
00:55:38,000 --> 00:55:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog vam je otvorio puteve i dao priliku, ali na vama je izbor da li ćete ići s tim putevne.

921
00:55:45,000 --> 00:55:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] I u podozirom zakonu, kad je mi Bog dao sve šta im treba, uvijem ih obličan u zemlji,

922
00:55:51,000 --> 00:55:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] daje mi potrebe zapovedi po kojima trebao živjeti, kaže volako:

923
00:55:56,000 --> 00:56:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gledaj, danas predate stavljam život i sreću, smrt i nesreću.

924
00:56:04,000 --> 00:56:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako poslušaš zapovedi Jahra, Boga svoga, koji ti danas dan,

925
00:56:10,000 --> 00:56:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] ako ih poslušaš ljubeći Jahra, Boga svoga,

926
00:56:13,000 --> 00:56:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hodeći njegovim putevima, vršeći njegove zapovede, njegove zakone, njegove uredbe,

927
00:56:19,000 --> 00:56:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] živjet ćeš i razdnožit će Jahra, Boga tvoja.

928
00:56:23,000 --> 00:56:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] I blagoslovit će te u zemlju u kojoj ulaziš da je zaposjetiš.

929
00:56:27,000 --> 00:56:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako se srce tvoje odradiš i ne poslušaš, nego zastraniš i budeš se klanjan drugim bogovima

930
00:56:36,000 --> 00:56:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] i njima iskazila oštovanje, ja vam danas izjavujem da ćete zaista proposti.

931
00:56:42,000 --> 00:56:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nećete dugo živjeti na zemlji u kojoj ćete prešavši i odmah ući da je zaposjetiš.

932
00:56:48,000 --> 00:56:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uzimam danas za svjedoke proti vas nebo i zemlje.

933
00:56:53,000 --> 00:57:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da predastavljam život i smrt, plagost i prokletstvo.

934
00:57:02,000 --> 00:57:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Život dakle bire, ljubeći Jahru Boga svoga, slušajući njegov glas, priranjajući uz njega da živiš ti i tvoje potustvo.

935
00:57:12,000 --> 00:57:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da on je život tvoj i tvoj dugi vijek, da bi mirno mnoga obaraviti na zemlji, za koju se Jahra zaklja ocima tvojem Adrachomu i za koju Jahru nećem dati.

936
00:57:23,000 --> 00:57:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ova riječ je tako aktualna za vas i to baš za ovaj period.

937
00:57:27,000 --> 00:57:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog danas i svaki nared danas stavlja pred tebe izbor.

938
00:57:32,000 --> 00:57:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] I daje ti savjest sine, hćenje, život prije.

939
00:57:36,000 --> 00:57:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubeći Jahru, prijavljujući njega.

940
00:57:39,000 --> 00:57:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne moraš biti savršen. Niti Bog očekuje da odbog postaneš savršeno trepustan, ali dođi svaki nared k njega.

941
00:57:46,000 --> 00:57:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Upoznaj ga.

942
00:57:48,000 --> 00:57:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pojačaj molim tvojom. Upoznaj ga riječi.

943
00:57:52,000 --> 00:57:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je učinio zadnjih pet godina u mojom životu toliko čude da ih ne mogu napravati više.

944
00:57:57,000 --> 00:57:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Doslice.

945
00:57:58,000 --> 00:58:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja vam garantijam da sve što ovdje piše ismo.

946
00:58:01,000 --> 00:58:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad što vam znamo je samo jednu valo knjižicu u biblije.

947
00:58:04,000 --> 00:58:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vinti koje je to bogatstvo.

948
00:58:07,000 --> 00:58:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Upoznajte ga.

949
00:58:09,000 --> 00:58:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on će vam posvijeziti vaše životne situacije i dati rješenja koje vam niste mogli prestanati.

950
00:58:14,000 --> 00:58:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dajte Bogu prilijepo.

951
00:58:16,000 --> 00:58:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

